4, \"to\": 1918}, {\"ngram\": \"Livestock Australia\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1940}, {\"ngram\": \"a one-line statement\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 1969}, {\"ngram\": \"Methandienone\", \"from\": 1992, \"to\": 2005}, {\"ngram\": \"any capacity\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2033}, {\"ngram\": \"any veterinary medicine\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2093}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cattle Australia's CEODr Chris Parkeralso confirmed that methandienone is not used in any capacity in Australian beef production, and added: \\\"We look forward to continuing to provide China and all our customers with nutritious high quality Australian beef.\\\"\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2354, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2104, \"end\": 2113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999991659641477, \"rank\": 6.803815397862229e-07, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 2199, \"end\": 2209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"score\": 0.9994284916307933, \"rank\": 0.0005701829480013055, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\"}, {\"begin\": 2280, \"end\": 2285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9337679695741891, \"rank\": 0.06773013026676811, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 2337, \"end\": 2347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"score\": 0.9994284916307933, \"rank\": 0.0005701829480013055, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chris Parkeralso\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2138}, {\"ngram\": \"methandienone\", \"from\": 2154, \"to\": 2167}, {\"ngram\": \"any capacity\", \"from\": 2183, \"to\": 2195}, {\"ngram\": \"all our customers\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2307}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Department of Agriculture, Fisheries and Forestry was also able to confirm to Beef that Menthandienone is not approved for use in Australian beef production.\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2517, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2490, \"end\": 2500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"score\": 0.9994284916307933, \"rank\": 0.0005701829480013055, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Department\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2370}, {\"ngram\": \"Agriculture\", \"from\": 2374, \"to\": 2385}, {\"ngram\": \"Fisheries\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2396}, {\"ngram\": \"Forestry\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2409}, {\"ngram\": \"Beef\", \"from\": 2438, \"to\": 2442}, {\"ngram\": \"Menthandienone\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2462}, {\"ngram\": \"use\", \"from\": 2483, \"to\": 2486}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Australia has a robust regulatory system and produces beef to meet importing country requirements,\\\" a Department spokesperson said in a statement.\", \"from\": 2519, \"to\": 2666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2520, \"end\": 2529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999991659641477, \"rank\": 6.803815397862229e-07, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 2622, \"end\": 2645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spokesperson_for_the_United_States_Department_of_State\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Department spokesperson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spokesperson_for_the_United_States_Department_of_State\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spokesperson_for_the_United_States_Department_of_State\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a robust regulatory system\", \"from\": 2534, \"to\": 2560}, {\"ngram\": \"beef\", \"from\": 2574, \"to\": 2578}, {\"ngram\": \"country requirements\", \"from\": 2597, \"to\": 2617}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 2654, \"to\": 2665}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Australian beef produced is safe for consumers.\\\"\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2717, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2669, \"end\": 2679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"score\": 0.9994284916307933, \"rank\": 0.0005701829480013055, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"consumers\", \"from\": 2706, \"to\": 2715}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Methandienone, also known as methandrostenolone, is sold under the brand name Dianabol (D-Bol) among others.\", \"from\": 2719, \"to\": 2827, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2797, \"end\": 2805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metandienone\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dianabol\", \"types\": [\"Q8386\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metandienone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metandienone\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Methandienone\", \"from\": 2719, \"to\": 2732}, {\"ngram\": \"methandrostenolone\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2766}, {\"ngram\": \"the brand name\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2796}, {\"ngram\": \"(D-Bol\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 2812}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 2826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is an androgen and anabolic steroid medication which is often used because of its effectiveness for bulking cycles.\", \"from\": 2828, \"to\": 2946, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an androgen and anabolic steroid medication\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2877}, {\"ngram\": \"its effectiveness\", \"from\": 2909, \"to\": 2926}, {\"ngram\": \"bulking cycles\", \"from\": 2931, \"to\": 2945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Methandienone has never been detected in Australian beef exports, despite countless residue screening tests in Australia and overseas over the past 30 years.\", \"from\": 2948, \"to\": 3105, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2989, \"end\": 2999, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"score\": 0.9994284916307933, \"rank\": 0.0005701829480013055, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\"}, {\"begin\": 3059, \"end\": 3068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999991659641477, \"rank\": 6.803815397862229e-07, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Methandienone\", \"from\": 2948, \"to\": 2961}, {\"ngram\": \"countless residue screening tests\", \"from\": 3022, \"to\": 3055}, {\"ngram\": \"the past 30 years\", \"from\": 3087, \"to\": 3104}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Veterinarians told Beef Central this morning that methandienone is used legitimately in human medicine around the world, and is a popular drug of choice among human body builders, but was not effective in beef cattle.\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3324, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Veterinarians\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3120}, {\"ngram\": \"Beef Central\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3138}, {\"ngram\": \"methandienone\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3170}, {\"ngram\": \"human medicine\", \"from\": 3195, \"to\": 3209}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3217, \"to\": 3226}, {\"ngram\": \"a popular drug\", \"from\": 3235, \"to\": 3249}, {\"ngram\": \"choice\", \"from\": 3253, \"to\": 3259}, {\"ngram\": \"human body builders\", \"from\": 3266, \"to\": 3285}, {\"ngram\": \"beef cattle\", \"from\": 3312, \"to\": 3323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It would make no sense to administer an unregistered compound like methandienone to cattle, when there are other anabolic steroids (testosterone derivatives) like trenbolone acetate (TBA) found in registered cattle growth promotants, which are permitted for use (in markets that accept HGP-treated cattle), are more effective in cattle, easier to obtain, cheaper and produce longer pay-outs,\\\" one experienced cattle vet said.\", \"from\": 3326, \"to\": 3752, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no sense\", \"from\": 3341, \"to\": 3349}, {\"ngram\": \"an unregistered compound\", \"from\": 3364, \"to\": 3388}, {\"ngram\": \"methandienone\", \"from\": 3394, \"to\": 3407}, {\"ngram\": \"cattle\", \"from\": 3411, \"to\": 3417}, {\"ngram\": \"other anabolic steroids\", \"from\": 3434, \"to\": 3457}, {\"ngram\": \"testosterone derivatives\", \"from\": 3459, \"to\": 3483}, {\"ngram\": \"trenbolone acetate\", \"from\": 3490, \"to\": 3508}, {\"ngram\": \"TBA\", \"from\": 3510, \"to\": 3513}, {\"ngram\": \"registered cattle growth promotants\", \"from\": 3524, \"to\": 3559}, {\"ngram\": \"use\", \"from\": 3585, \"to\": 3588}, {\"ngram\": \"markets\", \"from\": 3593, \"to\": 3600}, {\"ngram\": \"HGP-treated cattle\", \"from\": 3613, \"to\": 3631}, {\"ngram\": \"cattle\", \"from\": 3656, \"to\": 3662}, {\"ngram\": \"longer pay-outs\", \"from\": 3702, \"to\": 3717}, {\"ngram\": \"one experienced cattle vet\", \"from\": 3720, \"to\": 3746}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The fact it is not particularly effective in livestock is one reason why methandienone it is not registered for cattle,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3754, \"to\": 3884, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The fact\", \"from\": 3755, \"to\": 3763}, {\"ngram\": \"livestock\", \"from\": 3800, \"to\": 3809}